What is loop : Loop allows to run certain piece of code multiple times
Ex:
read 100 rows from excel
fetch 500 records from database
For loop:
for(initialize;condition;increment/decrement)
{
code/logic
}

while loop:
will executes if condition is true
while(condition)
{
logic
increment/decrement

}

